ygData.subject: LEVEL 20 ATLAST!
ygData.msgSnippet: Just thought that I d let everybody know that I have finally reached level 20! I did so last night while hunting in Najena. Level 19 had quite a splendid end
ygData.messageBody:
Just thought that I'd let everybody know that I
have finally reached level 20! I did so last night
while hunting in Najena. Level 19 had quite a splendid
end with the slaying of BoneCracker, whom gave me the
last bit of experience to level! I have yet to receive
my last name, I should be able tonight, but I am
still quite a happy Elf =) I am now getting ready to
return to my beloved Kelethin to train in the precious
skill of Double Attack, do some damage in Crushbone,
and show off a bit! See you all in
Norrath!<br><br>Trellan Hawksight, Wood Elf Ranger of 20 seasons
